{"tid":2104750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【初選．最後直路】All in 本土派  要大家繼續動員","createTime":"2020-07-12T07:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:39:58.000Z","uid":15846,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c744f7f5cfa577c9ea02e48e99df43fced29b66b","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"民主從來不告急，但一日未開票，冇人係夠票！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>連登集氣，全投本土抗爭派！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">港島 梁晃維/彭卓棋<br />\n九東 李嘉達/黃之鋒<br />\n九西 馮達浚/劉澤鋒/張崑陽<br />\n新東 鄒家成/劉頴匡/呂智恆<br />\n新西 張可森/黃子悅/伍健偉</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">超區全投坦克車王百羽</span><br />\n<br />\n四年前本民前入唔到去，四年後今日，後繼者全部都要贏初選、入議會！<br />\n<br />\n打足一年仗，今日我哋承受唔到任何一條戰線嘅失利，唔能夠再多四年挫敗，希望大家支持一班有堅定抗爭意志嘅參選人，揀班fit馬取代舊電池，入議會抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n可能好多人已經投咗，但你哋身邊仲有好多好多人未投。一個人<strong>share</strong>一個post，或者<strong>推</strong>一個post，就可以令到一百個人睇到，一定要繼續動員！谷恆個投票數字！"},{"pid":"53b110655880cb044719bfc0a0e63cb99cfe47cf","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"集氣！！！推！"},{"pid":"a9b1a6c083873378f98560a60326f110f8f0eae3","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"63e89a8b6690f8f392bb31a44ad3f51d1d1a7c7d","tid":2104750,"uid":193869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:42:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fed1ce2d06e27fbf0f375d8ea8884b0504eaa9de","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"高登可以推范國威入立法會，我哋要加油！！"},{"pid":"5458fe0e96b7adb1d47afd58bc3b42fa5222038a","tid":2104750,"uid":16135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10313e6364ce70a40e703f50b8908bdd6dd876e8","tid":2104750,"uid":39682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc0d82ff870857c8b006f58059015924d98e230","tid":2104750,"uid":193869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaee500663f407223b4786314a857e78dc4a5c95","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"255bd220e69cff2d4e27cb5faa965dedd7b3bc59","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗，踢走舊電池！"},{"pid":"9498c0bb24a9bd9734a3b176c00ed74540459f30","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:59:33.000Z","msg":"八鄉朱凱廸 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n【告別大黨時代  抗爭派一齊贏】<br />\n<br />\n新界西尚未投票的香港人，朱凱廸呼籲大家四人一組：<br />\n<br />\n一票伍健偉 天水連線<br />\n一票張可森 張可森 Sam Cheung<br />\n一票黃子悅 黃子悅<br />\n一票朱凱廸<br />\n<br />\n民主派議會路線，過去一直由大黨左右，今次民主派最大型的初選，除了是對共產黨的反擊，亦是對民主派路線的公投。2020年是香港人全面頑抗中共的時代，民主派亦應該擺脫「百貨應百客」的比例代表制束縛，告別大黨溫和路線，重建以抗爭者為主流的新民主派。<br />\n<br />\n新西抗爭派一齊贏！"},{"pid":"110b18f90330b2beb975902cd88c494d7fdaaaf1","tid":2104750,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080928795f9a52521d251585ee6e43ad0f3ff80a","tid":2104750,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:02:55.000Z","msg":"超區請投王百羽！"},{"pid":"fab06d6913d870c1adf01ac768348f3a39521f53","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb9fbead2d65a6b74946f5bc8685b7506f5fcf42","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:36:06.000Z","msg":"全投本土派"},{"pid":"804f5063601c91799ffc4f86d4b3854571658772","tid":2104750,"uid":15846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08:36:21.000Z","msg":"未完，唔好停！！！！！"},{"pid":"4ad4b83dd07e497580237c2b5